We're not taking the picture without Michael.

93
00:07:39,769 --> 00:07:42,325
- What's the matter, Sonny? - It's Michael.

94
00:08:31,268 --> 00:08:33,598
Don Barzini.

95
00:08:50,001 --> 00:08:53,230
Hey, Paulie!
Let me have some wine.

96
00:08:53,435 --> 00:08:55,731
Paulie! More wine.

97
00:08:56,035 --> 00:08:57,501
Scusi, please.

98
00:08:57,635 --> 00:08:59,101
You look terrific on the floor.

99
00:08:59,236 --> 00:08:59,792
What are you, a dance judge or something?

100
00:09:01,135 --> 00:09:04,999
Go take a walk around
the neighborhood. Do your job.

101
00:09:12,568 --> 00:09:15,432
Sandra, come on. Do me a favor. Watch the kids.

102
00:09:16,568 --> 00:09:19,501
- Don't let 'em run wild.
- You watch yourself, all right?

103
00:09:39,735 --> 00:09:42,098
Twenty or thirty grand.

104
00:09:42,268 --> 00:09:44,201
In small bills, cash.

105
00:09:44,869 --> 00:09:47,357
In that little silk purse.

106
00:09:47,535 --> 00:09:50,559
If this was somebody else's wedding.

107
00:09:51,136 --> 00:09:53,795
Hey, Paulie! I got two gobbagool...

108
