Stupid jerk!

110
00:10:06,636 --> 00:10:08,567
Hey, what's the matter?

111
00:10:20,702 --> 00:10:22,691
Have to go back to work.

112
00:10:23,102 --> 00:10:23,897
It's part of the wedding.

113
00:10:24,102 --> 00:10:27,466
No Sicilian can refuse any request
on his daughter's wedding day.

114
00:10:33,435 --> 00:10:35,833
