Get outta here.

117
00:10:44,735 --> 00:10:46,429
This is a private party. Go on.

118
00:10:47,569 --> 00:10:49,830
What is it? Hey, my sister's wedding.

119
00:10:57,102 --> 00:10:59,659
Goddamn FBI don't respect nothin'.

120
