Godfather, I have a daughter.

129
00:11:39,736 --> 00:11:42,963
See, she and Enzo...

130
00:11:43,236 --> 00:11:45,203
You want Enzo to stay in this country...

131
00:11:45,402 --> 00:11:48,335
