132
00:11:48,870 --> 00:11:50,994
You understand everything.

133
00:11:52,102 --> 00:11:54,898
Mr. Hagen. Thank you.

134
00:11:57,770 --> 00:11:59,167
And wait till you see the beautiful wedding cake...

135
00:11:59,369 --> 00:12:00,494
