so he wanted to thank you.

146
00:13:03,403 --> 00:13:05,335
All right.

147
00:13:05,636 --> 00:13:08,363
Don Corleone, I am honored and grateful...

148
00:13:08,536 --> 00:13:10,900
that you have invited me to your home...

149
00:13:11,170 --> 00:13:13,761
on the wedding day of your daughter.

150
