221
00:19:38,972 --> 00:19:41,097
he wanted to get out of it.

222
00:19:41,904 --> 00:19:44,496
Now, Johnny is my father's godson...

223
00:19:44,805 --> 00:19:47,793
and my father went to see this bandleader...

224
00:19:48,138 --> 00:19:51,071
and he offered him $10,000 to let Johnny go.

225
00:19:52,104 --> 00:19:54,229
But the bandleader said no.

226
00:19:54,905 --> 00:19:57,995
So the next day my father went to see him...

227
00:19:58,371 --> 00:20:00,997
only this time with Luca Brasi.

228
00:20:01,571 --> 00:20:05,663
And within an hour, he signed a release...

229
00:20:07,571 --> 00:20:10,799
for a certified check of $1,000.

230
00:20:11,972 --> 00:20:13,699
How'd he do that?

231
00:20:13,904 --> 00:20:16,393
My father made him an offer he couldn't refuse.

232
00:20:17,405 --> 00:20:19,633
