240
00:21:13,639 --> 00:21:15,797
Give him a glass of wine.

241
00:21:35,371 --> 00:21:37,167
I'll take care of it.

242
00:21:39,673 --> 00:21:42,604
I want you to find Santino.
Tell him to come to the office.

243
00:21:50,205 --> 00:21:52,068
